## Summary

📋 **Test List Created:**

**Feature**: Game of Life CLI Kata
**Test File**: src/game-of-life.spec.ts
**Base Functionality Tests**: 10

**Test Cases** (ordered simple → complex):
1. ✅ Empty configuration returns no living cells
2. ✅ Zero steps returns configuration unchanged
3. ✅ Single lonely cell dies after 1 step
4. ✅ Two isolated cells die after 1 step
5. ✅ Cell with 2-3 neighbors survives (basic survival)
6. ✅ Dead cell with exactly 3 neighbors becomes alive (birth rule)
7. ✅ Stable block pattern (2x2) remains unchanged
8. ✅ Output is lexicographically sorted (x ascending, y ascending)
9. ✅ Negative coordinates are handled correctly
10. ✅ Rules apply iteratively across multiple steps

